### 📄 Corrected `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AuraEcho+ — .gitignore
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── SECRET FILES — NEVER COMMIT ──────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.staging

# Firebase credentials
database/firebase_credentials.json
data/firebase_credentials.json
*_credentials.json
*_service_account.json

# Certificates & Keys
*.pem
*.key

# ── Python ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
eggs/
parts/
var/
sdist/
develop-eggs/
.installed.cfg
lib/
lib64/

# ── Virtual Environments ─────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
.env/

# ── Testing & Coverage ───────────────────────────────────────────
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.tox/
*.coveragerc

# ── Databases (local data — not for version control) ─────────────
database/*.db
database/*.sqlite
database/*.sqlite3
database/records_backup.csv

# ── ML Models & Scalers (regenerated from data) ──────────────────
# FIXED: Path changed from data/models/ to models/
models/
models/*.pkl
models/*.joblib
models/*.h5

# ── Export files ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
data/exports/
*.csv.export

# ── Streamlit ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.streamlit/
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# ── IDE & Editor ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
auraecho.log

# ── Jupyter ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# ── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
```

### ✅ Summary of Changes

| Change | Type | Reason |
|--------|------|--------|
| `data/models/` → `models/` | 🔧 Fixed | Matches `MODEL_SAVE_PATH` in `constants.py` |
| Added `database/firebase_credentials.json` | ➕ Added | Matches expected credentials path |
| Added `auraecho.log` | ➕ Added | Matches `LOG_FILE` in `constants.py` |
| Added `database/records_backup.csv` | ➕ Added | Matches `LOCAL_CSV_BACKUP_PATH` |
| Added `.streamlit/` | ➕ Added | Ignores entire Streamlit config directory |
| Removed `data/models/` | 🔴 Removed | No longer used |

This `.gitignore` is now **fully aligned** with your codebase and will prevent accidental commits of sensitive data, logs, and generated files. 🚀

